headline: Netflix & UnitedHealth earnings, housing data: What to Watch
summary: Key earnings from Taiwan Semiconductor (TSM), UnitedHealth Group (UNH), American Express (AXP), and Netflix (NFLX) are set to be released Thursday, with Netflix no longer reporting its quarterly subscriber numbers. March housing data is also due, with economists forecasting declines in starts and permits. Meanwhile, markets are watching for more Federal Reserve commentary after Fed Chairman Jerome Powell’s remarks on Wednesday deepened a sell-off. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.
